# 🇮🇳 Trade Intelligence Engine
# .gitignore — Reviewed and fixed for Streamlit Cloud deployment
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WHAT CHANGED FROM YOUR ORIGINAL:
#   + Added .streamlit/secrets.toml          ← CRITICAL — your API keys
#   + Added data/                            ← datasets stay local
#   + Added *.xls *.xlsx (data files)        ← ITC TradeMap files
#   + Added *.json in data/ context          ← HS/duty JSON datasets
#   + Added gemini_test.py                   ← local test file, not for prod
#   + Added *.docx *.pdf (generated reports) ← don't commit binary outputs
#   + Tightened .env to cover all variants
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🔐 SECRETS — NEVER COMMIT THESE (your app breaks AND gets hacked)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Local .env file (contains NVIDIA_API_KEY, SUPABASE keys, SMTP passwords)
.env
.env.*
.env.local
.env.production
.envrc

# Streamlit secrets file (on Streamlit Cloud you use the Secrets UI instead)
.streamlit/secrets.toml

# Any file named secrets
*secrets*
*secret*


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📊 DATA FILES — Keep local, NOT in Git (too large, may be proprietary)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ITC TradeMap dataset
data/
*.xls
*.xlsx

# HS Code / duty / GST JSON datasets (built from government sources)
# These live in data/ which is already ignored above — but be explicit:
# data/hs_codes.json
# data/duty_structure.json
# data/gst_rates.json
# Note: data/ folder itself is ignored — no need to list individually


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🐍 PYTHON
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
*.pyd

# Distribution / packaging
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
share/python-wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg
MANIFEST

# Virtual environments
.venv
venv/
env/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/
.pixi
__pypackages__/

# PyInstaller
*.manifest
*.spec

# Testing / coverage
htmlcov/
.tox/
.nox/
.coverage
.coverage.*
.cache
nosetests.xml
coverage.xml
*.cover
*.py.cover
.hypothesis/
